abstract: New York Jets sign running backs Matt Forte, Bilal Powell and Khiry Robinson; have not re-signed starting quarterback Ryan Fitzpatrick.
lead_paragraph: The Jets have secured their top three running backs for next season, but Ryan Fitzpatrick is still a free agent.

headline.main: Jets Build Running Corps, but Still Lack a Quarterback
headline.print_headline: Jets Build Running Corps, but Still Lack a Quarterback
